Conclusion:







These data indicate that CRO 11-vcMMAE can be a highly potent and selective agent for the treatment of astrocytoma/glioblastoma and their metastasis as well as brain tumors of medulloblastoma and neuroectodermal origin. CRO11-vcMMAE can also be useful for the treatment of melanoma metastasis to brain and other brain neoplasms such as neoplastic meningitis.







